<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Welcome to Codeforces</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #1a75ff;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      color: #666;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      color: white;
      background-color: #1a75ff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to Codeforces!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{email}},</p>
    
    <p>We're excited to welcome you to the Codeforces platform! Your account has been successfully created and you're now part of our competitive programming community.</p>
    
    <p>Here are a few things you can do to get started:</p>
    
    <ul>
      <li>Complete your profile</li>
      <li>Browse upcoming contests</li>
      <li>Solve practice problems</li>
      <li>Join discussions</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
    
    <p>Happy coding!</p>
    
    <p>The Codeforces Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>This email was sent to {{email}}. If you didn't create a Codeforces account, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p>&copy; {{year}} Codeforces. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
